1.3 Support for learning

This resource is designed to enable independent, self-paced learning. However, additional benefits
may be gained by using it in partnership with other resources and supports, such as research supervi-
sors, fellow research students, research librarians, or other training providers.

     QUT only
     Do you have a burning question or need more help?
     Your Liaison Librarian is a critical part of your HDR support team. Contact them with any questions about
     your AIRS assessment or anything else. They are here to help you!

