To help expand your search terms, you can create a concept map or mind map, like the example near
the top of this page, which situates the research question in the centre of the map and graphically rep-
resents the associated research concepts. This can help you to clarify the logic of these concepts and
illustrate their relationships with your keywords, synonyms, and related terms.
Alternatively, you may like to organise the information in a table as demonstrated below with our
example research question:

