   papers to help you evaluate their relevance to     tool has been trained. As a result, they can provide
   your research or to compare and evaluate how       incorrect and inaccurate information, analysis, and
   you have interpreted a research paper              references (also known as hallucinations)

· AI tools can automate repetitive tasks, such as  · AI tools are unable to reproduce results or explain
   data collection, cleaning, and organisation,       how they came to an answer
   thereby allowing more time for higher-level
   analysis and interpretation                     · More tools are being placed behind paywalls, which
                                                      can make accessing them difficult and costly

