                          them online here: https://qut.pressbooks.pub/airs/?p=926#oembed-1

                                    Keeping up to date with current literature and emerging research (QUT YouTube video, 1m11s).

There are many different types of alerts, many of which can be accessed by registering with your
favourite databases or Google Scholar.
